						               													<description>Game Design is a tableau building game about designing a game. Players need to build their own game project of their best. Designing schedule, collecting ideas and demonstrating their games to the game enthusiasts.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game consists of three rounds,and each round is with three turns. For the beginning of every round, players get four idea cards and do card drafting. In each turn, you and your opponents choose a flowchart tile and do the possible actions: (1) play a new idea card from your hand to expand your design, (2) collect resource from your design where your personal meeple is located, or (3)demonstrate part of your design(mechanic, theme or art) and get feedback, which mean your scores.&amp;#10;  &amp;#10;Every part of your game design shows the fame and the possibilities of your project. The game ends when all flowchart tiles are played. The winner belongs to who has the highest scores and will have the chance to publish the design.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
